  icon: {fileID: -5335637903981835044, guid: c2423ea8241314f43b051a60e71df168, type: 3}
  fullArt: {fileID: -5335637903981835044, guid: c2423ea8241314f43b051a60e71df168, type: 3}
  subtitle: 'Ndugu''s Gift '
  journalDescription: 'These boots carry the weight of

    eleven days without food
    and an

    Arctic that shrinks a little more

    every summer.


    Bjorn
    left them without looking back.

    That is the most he will ever say

    about
    needing help.


    Move faster. Cover more ground.

    Do not stop.


    EFFECT:
    + 1 movement speed'
